<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h3 id="head-20b8a3b4fb580aa7e366b5d611fbe576b0988053">Nirnaeth Arnoediad</h3>
For thaumaturgists who prefers breezing through this level: <p>
Just cast gravity spells to move monsters out of the way. You would need lots of speed though. 
</p>
<hr>
 For thaumaturgists who prefers clearing out this level: <p>
This Gondolin quest can be accomplished easily even at relatively low levels (20+). If you manage to get nifty View or Area spells and terrain-altering non-view spells (fire or water). The challenge here is to get those nasty Hrus away from you, since all the others can be killed easily enough. 
</p>
<p>
Cast the terrain-altering spells repeatedly until you are completely surrounded by lava or water (preferably at your starting corner). Since most of the trolls including hrus can't cross these types of terrain, they won't be able to reach you. You're now free to fire away at the trolls with your view and area spells. Beware of the dragons though (and Ulik too IIRC), because they can fly over lava and water. <h3 id="head-ff11f0da0a4cd245270f188d8a7299b4084d0328">Chatter</h3>

</p>
